52:24.809 --> 52:28.604
♪ ’Cause you make me feel ♪

52:28.688 --> 52:31.649
BOTH:
♪ You make me feel ♪

52:31.732 --> 52:36.112
♪ You make me feel like ♪

52:36.195 --> 52:39.282
♪ A natural woman ♪

52:40.908 --> 52:42.034
♪ Woman. ♪

