53:18.237 --> 53:21.407
♪ Before the day I met you ♪

53:21.490 --> 53:24.243
♪ Life was so unkind ♪

53:24.327 --> 53:28.873
♪ But you’re the key
to my peace of mind ♪

53:28.956 --> 53:32.293
♪ ’Cause you make me feel ♪

53:32.376 --> 53:35.171
♪ You make me feel ♪

53:35.254 --> 53:38.090
♪ You make me feel like ♪

53:38.174 --> 53:42.094
♪ A natural woman ♪

53:42.178 --> 53:44.639
♪ Woman ♪

53:44.722 --> 53:48.726
♪ When my soul
was in the lost and found ♪

53:49.977 --> 53:51.062
♪ Ah-ooh ♪

53:51.145 --> 53:55.149
♪ You came along to claim it ♪

53:56.400 --> 53:57.526
♪ Ah-ooh ♪

